p: The AChE inhibitory activity of the two EOs is shown in Fig 3. The ANOVA showed significant differences between the inhibitory activity of the two EOs ( F 1, 28 = 60.140; P < 0.001), with a significant effect of the dose ( F 6, 28 = 315.589; P < 0.001) and the interaction oil x dosage ( F 6, 28 = 4.512; P = 0.003).
